{"tid":25931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"內地口音女同學:我想食賓周","createTime":"2016-12-06T12:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T13:16:25.000Z","uid":21598,"like":9,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da5d199351662f82e260584c7fe4dd15ce5b7599","tid":25931,"uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n琴日放學我同一個充滿內地口音既女同學去我佢屋企做PROJECT <br />\n佢行行下突然同我講:我想食賓周 <br />\n心諗:平時斯斯文文,原來你咁撚OPEN 架? <br />\n我即刻扯哂,我20cm既賓周就表露無遺 <br />\n<br />\n我見佢樣貌都算OK,只有d內地口音.有得食當然食啦 <br />\n去到佢屋企,佢話去toilet. <br />\n我當然即刻衝入去佢間房上佢張床, <br />\n<br />\n我除哂衫褲,訓係佢張床等佢 <br />\n隻手不斷搓弄我20cm的陽具 <br />\n心諗:佢一定會見到我有20cm而開心 <br />\n<br />\n當佢出黎個陣,佢走左入廚房打開個雪櫃拎左D野 <br />\n唔通玩冰火!? <br />\n<br />\n當女同學走入黎既時候 佢見到我除左衫,見到我20cm既陽具O 哂嘴 <br />\n唔通佢見到我咁大而呆左? <br />\n<br />\n點知原來佢隻手拎住一條雪冰左既&quot;冰蕉&quot; <br />\n<br />\n原來佢係想食冰蕉,唔係賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後個女同學驚到走左出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e836fb03764d35351d626fb09f7a874af780a3","tid":25931,"uid":2477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"有是咁的，但創意略欠<br />\n65 分"},{"pid":"48eb403c28e6ff1717979123643a462bea4db8f9","tid":25931,"uid":17682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"零分重作"},{"pid":"c0510d6648dce03b689e8332354b723cf8c09445","tid":25931,"uid":4724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply